videos.description: Ryan Nall run for 12-yards for a TD (Garrett Owens KICK)
videos.headline: OSU opens up scoring on Ryan Nall TD run

videos.description: Oregon RB Tony Brooks-James runs up the middle for the 3-yard score
videos.headline: Quack Attack answer back with James TD run

videos.description: Ian Wheeler punt for 31 yds , Victor Bolden Jr. muffs fumble return but tips the loose ball forward for teammates to jump on it
videos.headline: Oregon State muffs punt return but recovers

videos.description: Marcus McMaryion pass complete to Victor Bolden Jr. for 5-yards Victor Bolden Jr. fumbled, forced by Arrion Springs, recovered by Oregn Justin Hollins
videos.headline: Ducks DB Arrion Springs rips ball away from Beaver WR

videos.description: Oregon's Jalen Brown gets the ball on the reverse and then throws it deep to Darren Carrington II for a 33-yard touchdown to give the Ducks a lead in the Civil War.
videos.headline: Ducks get tricky with reverse pass for TD

videos.description: Marcus McMaryion pass complete to Ricky Ortiz for 6-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Beavers tie it up, find TE wide open in the flat

videos.description: Oregon RB Tony Brooks-James fumbles, Oregon ST recovers
videos.headline: Oregon drive stalls following RB fumble

videos.description: Justin Herbert rolls out and finds Charles Nelson for 23-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Charles Nelson makes leaping grab to give Ducks lead

videos.description: Ryan Nall run for 14-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Beavers pull within three on Nall's second rushing TD

videos.description: Marcus McMaryion run for 33-yards to the Oregn 38 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Beavers burst into Duck territory on QB keeper

videos.description: Ryan Nall run for 6-yards for a TD. Ruling on field confirmed following review.
videos.headline: Ryan Nall lunges forward to give OSU the lead

videos.description: Oregon State finally ends their losing streak to Oregon with Ryan Nall punching it in for his fourth touchdown of the game to put the Beavers up 34-24.
videos.headline: Nall's TD seals Civil War win for Oregon State

videos.description: Justin Herbert pass complete to Darren Carrington II for 26-yards to the OrgSt 45 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Oregon WR Darren Carrington makes terrific over the shoulder catch
